`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Hide
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * hide

 Hide lets a character hide unseen in a room, while remaining stationary.
Performing most "active" actions will stop the effect, as will the visible
command. Players and mobiles affected by the detect hidden spell will also be
able to see anyone hiding.

